	<tr>
		
			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				I know this post is a little off, but someone had posted earlier about faction to get the Aegis Of Life shield quest.<BR>
<BR>
To gain faction with Camlend in the Temple of Life in Qeynos, go to the bank, get 250 Platinum, and convert it to gold.  Head on over to the Temple of Life and Hail Lashun Novashine.  Give Lashun Novashine 2 pieces of gold at a time until you have gone completely through the 250 Plats that you converted to gold.  Each time you give hime the gold, you get a faction increase with the Temple of Life. <BR>
<BR>
You may have to occasionally hail Lashun Novashine, as he tends to want to wander about.  My faction was dubious when I first entered Qeynos, and doing this raised my faction high enough to get the quest for the Aegis Of Life shield.  <BR>
<BR>
Aaldolur Shadowdancer<BR>
Cleric of the 39th Season<BR>
Bertoxxulous Server
				</font>
